title: ASMR Stye Treatment
description: ASMR Stye Treatment is a beauty game where you must treat your patient's dirty pimply face to make it healthy again. Be the pimple popper doctor and help her to take care of her face problem. Go live and show this satisfying pimple pooping to the world. After finishing the face treatment, style our patient with the best outfit and makeup from our collections to create the perfect look!
